manifests.contents:
bench = []
test = []
example = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "hcloudfirewallupdater"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "hcloudfirewallupdater"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"

[dependencies]
env_logger = "0.11"
log = "0.4"
serde_json = "1"
trust-dns-resolver = "0.23"

[dependencies.clap]
version = "4"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.reqwest]
version = "0.12"
features = ["json", "rustls-tls"]

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1"
features = ["full"]

[profile.release]
opt-level = "z"
lto = true
strip = true

[profile.release.package]
